  "label": "Sevrin Halcott",
  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human of bronze skinTone and a compact, work-hardened build shaped by long years of service behind a bar. Brown eyes sit deep beneath a broad brow, giving a steady, appraising regard that rarely shifts in company. Brown hair, kept in a short and practical style, frames a square face marked by permanent smile-lines and a clearly set jaw. The hands are notably thick-fingered and calloused, a defining sign of repetitive labor and frequent handling of heavy casks and glassware.",
